<li><a href='https://ssciwr.github.io/jupyter-data-exploration/pandas-toy-data.html'>Part 2</a></li>
<li><a href='https://ssciwr.github.io/jupyter-data-exploration/pandas-real-data.html'>Part 3</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="slides">
{%- endblock body_header -%}
